update.description:
This pull request depends on pull request #8, review that one first. It uses a ruby library `ffi` to call C functions to do the real work.

# Examples

```
$ ign fuel list             
Error in REST request
http://localhost:8001/trudy/tm1
http://localhost:8001/trudy/tm2
http://localhost:8001/trudy/tm3
http://localhost:8001/bob/bm2
http://localhost:8001/bob/bm1
http://localhost:8001/bob/bm3
http://localhost:8001/alice/am1
http://localhost:8001/alice/am2
http://localhost:8001/alice/am3
```

```
$ ign fuel list --name am1
http://localhost:8001/alice/am1
```

```
$ ign fuel list --owner bob 
http://localhost:8001/bob/bm2
http://localhost:8001/bob/bm1
http://localhost:8001/bob/bm3
```

```
$ ign fuel pull --owner asdf --name asdf
TODO Download a model
```

```
$ ign fuel push --owner asdf --name asdf --url todo --path /tmp/asdf
TODO Upload a model
```

```
$ ign fuel locate --name am3
/build/ign-fuel-tools/local/alice/am3
```
update.title: ign-tool integration

update.description:
This pull request depends on pull request #8, review that one first

#Goals

* `ign fuel ...` working with `FuelClient.cc`
    * `ign fuel list ...` Lists available models
    * `ign fuel push ...` Uploads a model to a server
    * `ign fuel pull ...` Downloads a model from a server


#Plan

* Use ruby library `ffi` to call C functions to do the real work
* Make a C wrapper around the C++ library
    * C functions will write directly to stdout


#Current state

```
$ ign fuel list             
Error in REST request
http://localhost:8001/trudy/tm1
http://localhost:8001/trudy/tm2
http://localhost:8001/trudy/tm3
http://localhost:8001/bob/bm2
http://localhost:8001/bob/bm1
http://localhost:8001/bob/bm3
http://localhost:8001/alice/am1
http://localhost:8001/alice/am2
http://localhost:8001/alice/am3
```

```
$ ign fuel list --name am1
http://localhost:8001/alice/am1
```

```
$ ign fuel list --owner bob 
http://localhost:8001/bob/bm2
http://localhost:8001/bob/bm1
http://localhost:8001/bob/bm3
```

```
$ ign fuel pull --owner asdf --name asdf
TODO Download a model
```

```
$ ign fuel push --owner asdf --name asdf --url todo --path /tmp/asdf
TODO Upload a model
```
